name: Monroe Preserve
address: 102 Monroe Preserve Lane, Chapin, South Carolina 29036
description:
ABOUT THE HOME ENERGY RATING SCALE
The HERS (Home Energy Rating System) Index allows buyers to compare the relative energy efficiency of different homes. The HERS Index home energy rating is determined by an independent RESNET-certified home energy rater ("Rater"). The lower a home’s score, the more energy efficient it is in comparison to the HERS referenced home. For every one-point decrease in the HERS Index score, there is a corresponding one percent (1%) reduction in energy consumption as compared to a home with a HERS Index of 100. A home with a HERS score of 100 reflects a home built to 2006 IEEC Building Codes. See the bottom of this page for more information on HERS scores.

amenities.name: Enjoy convenient
amenities.description: Enjoy convenient access to I-26, aiding in a smooth work commute and enhancing work-life balance.

amenities.name: Every new
amenities.description: Every new Pulte home is a smart home, offering superior Wi-Fi coverage and a full suite of automation options that truly bring your home to life.

amenities.name: Multiple parks
amenities.description: Multiple parks are nearby, including Melvin Park, Dreher Island State Park, Crooked Creek Park, Rocky Branch Natural Area, and Hilton Recreation Area.

amenities.name: Lake Murray
amenities.description: Lake Murray offers public docks and boat ramps less than 15 minutes from your new home in Monroe Preserve.

amenities.name: Dine Chophouse
amenities.description: Dine at Chophouse of Chapin, 518 Smokehouse, Liberty Tap Room & Grill, Catch 22, Bakon Southern Eatery, Higher Ground Char House, and more, all just miles from your new home community.

amenities.name: Home Designs
amenities.description: Pulte Homes come with an industry-leading 10-year limited structural new home warranty.

amenities.name: Our time-tested
amenities.description: Our time-tested Build Quality Experience process ensures the highest quality and customer satisfaction.

amenities.name: Store your
amenities.description: Store your boat at Lighthouse Marina.

amenities.name: Less than
amenities.description: Less than 5 miles from the Chapin Equestrian Center.

amenities.name: Enjoy incredible
amenities.description: Enjoy incredible attractions such as the Spirit of Lake Murray sunset cruise or the Pilot Cove Ventures Sail Tour.

amenities.name: Play round
amenities.description: Play a round of golf at the Mid Carolina Club, which is open for non-members as well.

amenities.name: Bring home
